SwitchStorage
Usage: SwitchStorage
Switches the display between furniture store
and personal storage.
---
OpenMessage
Usage: OpenMessage [index]
Opens a conversation indicated by index
(in the order of appearance in display).
---
CloseMessage
Usage: CloseMessage
Closes the opened conversation.
---
ReadAll
Usage: ReadAll
Marks all conversations as read.
---
ScrollDown
usage: ScrollDown [displayIdx]
Scrolls down the indicated display
---
ScrollUp
Usage: ScrollUp [displayIdx]
Scrolls up the indicated display
---
ShowFurniture
Usage: ShowFurniture [aptIdx] [roomIdx]
Switches the furniture display to the indicated room.
---
ShowRooms
Usage: ShowRooms [aptIdx]
Switches the rooms display to the indicated apartment.
---
ShowApartment
Usage: ShowApartment [aptIdx]
Switches the apartment display to the indicated apartment.
---
SplitRoomVertically
Usage: SplitRoomVertically [aptIdx] [roomIdx] [y]
Cost: 50, Time: 20
Splits the indicated room into two on the given
y axis.
---
SplitRoomHorizontally
Usage: SplitRoomHorizontally [aptIdx] [roomIdx] [x]
Cost: 50, Time: 20
Splits the indicated room into two on the given
x axis.
---
MergeRooms
Usage: MergeRooms [aptIdx] [roomIdx] [roomIdx]
Cost: 50, Time: 20
Merges the indicated rooms into one.
---
PlaceFurniture
Usage: PlaceFurniture [aptIdx] [roomIdx] [furnIdx] [x] [y]
Places furniture from storage into the indicated room.
---
RemoveFurniture
Usage: RepairFurniture [aptIdx] [roomIdx] [furnIdx]
Removes indicated furniture from the room and places
it in storage.
---
RepairFurniture
Usage: RepairFurniture [aptIdx] [roomIdx] [furnIdx]
Time: 30 (successful)/5 (insufficient balance)
Repairs indicated furniture to perfect condition.
---
ChangeRoomColor
Usage: ChangeRoomColor [aptIdx] [roomIdx] [r] [g] [b]
Changes the room color to a given rgb value.
---
ChangeRoomName
Usage: ChangeRoomName [aptIdx] [roomIdx]
Changes the room name.
---
SplitVertically
Usage: SplitVertically [aptIdx] [y]
Cost: 100, Time: 60
Splits the indicated apartment into two on the given
y axis.
---
SplitHorizontally
Usage: SplitHorizontally [aptIdx] [x]
Cost: 100, Time: 60
Splits the indicated apartment into two on the given
x axis.
---
Merge
Usage: Merge [aptIdx] [aptIdx]
Cost: 100, Time: 60
Merges the indicated apartments into one.
---
Market
Usage: Merge [aptIdx] [rent]
Cost: 5, Time: 10
Puts the indicated apartment on the market with given rent.
---
ChangeRent
Usage: ChangeRent [tenantIdx] [rent]
Changes the rent on the lease to a new value.
---
Renew
Usage: ChangeRent [tenantIdx] [time]
Renews the rent for the indicated amount of time.
---
RotateFurniture
Usage: RotateFurniture [furnIdx]
Rotates indicated furniture in storage by 90 degrees.
---
SellFurniture
Usage: SellFurniture [furnIdx]
Time: 5
Sells indicated furniture to the store.
---
BuyFurniture
Usage: BuyFurniture [furnIdx]
Purchases indicated furniture from the store.
---